title: Why Warehouse is the unexpected high street gem to discover now - just ask the Duchess of Cambridge
text:
We love shining a spotlight on the unsung heroes of our Great British High Street. As much as we love Mango, Topshop and Zara, they tend to dominate when it comes to the high street's most-spotted pieces of the season - and there's a lot to be said for other brands, where we can purchase a sleek blazer or pretty printed frock that not everyone else will have.

Warehouse is one such humblebrag brand, and it's long been a hit with fashion editors thanks to its high quality and reasonable prices. Its slick autumn offering has put the brand high up on our new season shopping lists, and it seems we're not the only ones adding to basket. Here's why you should be shopping in Warehouse this autumn... ...
description: We love shining a spotlight on the unsung heroes of our Great British High Street.
